      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey just thinking about my supplement routine for the winter since it's so dark here in oslo. i was reading online that taking like 50,000 iu of vitamin d every day for a month or two could really help my immune system and energy levels. do u think that's a safe way to do a quick boost?",
